    <p>Per Lunde Jørgensen was born in Aarhus, Denmark (1964) and he lives and work in Copenhagen.  He holds an MFA from the Royal Danish Academy of Fine Arts, and has had several solo shows at Galleri Søren Houmann and at The Danish Cultural Ministery´s Kunsthal O-Overgaden.  
